details.name: Slithereen Crush
details.description: Slams the ground, stunning and damaging nearby enemy land units.  After the stun, the affected units are slowed. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Creates a puddle of water that is considered a river for bonuses. Provides 25 HP regen, 12 armor and 40% status resistance while in a puddle or in the river.
